### Levels

| Level | Use For                          |
|-------|----------------------------------|
| debug | development troubleshooting      |
| info  | significant operations           |
| warn  | recoverable issues, deprecations |
| error | failures needing attention       |

### Usage

Attach context ids to every log: `{ userId, requestId, [relevant ids] }`.

